      <title>快速搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/article/ecd1925.html"/>
      <url>/article/ecd1925.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="快速搭建漂亮的个人博客"><a href="#快速搭建漂亮的个人博客" class="headerlink" title="快速搭建漂亮的个人博客"></a>快速搭建漂亮的个人博客</h1><ul><li>vscode</li><li>markdown</li><li><a href="https://github.com/">github</a></li><li><a href="https://hexo.io/">hexo</a><h2 id="为什么需要一个独立的博客？"><a href="#为什么需要一个独立的博客？" class="headerlink" title="为什么需要一个独立的博客？"></a>为什么需要一个独立的博客？</h2></li></ul><ol><li>本地markdown管理文章文件，真正将自己的文章把我在自己的手中，随意可以导出到任何平台上</li><li>没有广告</li><li>有自己的域名</li><li>有丰富的主题可以选择</li></ol><h1 id="开始搭建"><a href="#开始搭建" class="headerlink" title="开始搭建"></a>开始搭建</h1><p>安装git</p><ul><li>Windows:  <a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win">git</a>.</li><li>Mac: 用 <a href="https://brew.sh/">Homebrew</a>, <a href="https://www.macports.org/">MacPorts</a> 或 <a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/git-osx-installer/">installer</a>安装.</li><li>Linux (Ubuntu, Debian): sudo apt-get install git-core</li><li>Linux (Fedora, Red Hat, CentOS): sudo yum install git-core</li></ul><p>安装node.js</p><ul><li>Windows: Install it with <a href="https://github.com/jasongin/nvs/">nvs</a> (recommended) or <a href="https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm">nvm</a>.</li><li>Mac: 用 <a href="https://brew.sh/">Homebrew</a>, <a href="https://www.macports.org/">MacPorts</a> 或 <a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/git-osx-installer/">installer</a>安装.</li><li>Linux (DEB/RPM-based): Install it with NodeSource.</li><li>其他: Install it through respective package manager. Refer to the guide provided by Node.js.</li></ul><h2 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h2><blockquote><p>npm install hexo-cli -g</p></blockquote><p>初始化（空目录）</p><blockquote><p>hexo init</p></blockquote><p>查看效果</p><blockquote><p>hexo s</p></blockquote><h2 id="github"><a href="#github" class="headerlink" title="github"></a>github</h2><ol><li><a href="https://github.com/new">新建repository</a></li><li>设置settings-&gt;pages</li><li>添加CNAME文件</li><li><a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">配置主题</a></li><li><a href="https://mengd.js.org/article/Quick-start.html">https://mengd.js.org/article/Quick-start.html</a></li><li>安装git插件<blockquote><p>npm install hexo-deployer-git –save</p></blockquote></li><li>生成html<blockquote><p>hexo g</p></blockquote></li><li>部署页面<blockquote><p>hexo d</p></blockquote></li></ol><h2 id="可能会遇到的问题"><a href="#可能会遇到的问题" class="headerlink" title="可能会遇到的问题"></a>可能会遇到的问题</h2><h3 id="配置github-ssh-keygen"><a href="#配置github-ssh-keygen" class="headerlink" title="配置github ssh-keygen"></a>配置github ssh-keygen</h3><ol><li>ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C “邮箱地址@qq.com”<blockquote><p>注意：自定义保存地址选择 /Users/用户名/.ssh/github_rsa</p></blockquote></li><li>修改~/.ssh 中的config文件</li><li>vim ～/.ssh/config<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Host github</span><br><span class="line">User git </span><br><span class="line">HostName github.com</span><br><span class="line">PreferredAuthentications publickey</span><br><span class="line">IdentityFile ~/.ssh/github_rsa</span><br><span class="line">ServerAliveInterval 300</span><br><span class="line">ServerAliveCountMax 10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>ssh-add -K ~/.ssh/github_rsa</li><li>pbcopy &lt; ~/.ssh/github_rsa.pub</li></ol><h3 id="链接优化"><a href="#链接优化" class="headerlink" title="链接优化"></a>链接优化</h3><blockquote><p>npm install hexo-abbrlink –save</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
